{"tid":1497261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"iPhone恐怖隱藏版功能 男友50天行蹤無所遁形","createTime":"2019-08-23T01:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:24:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb633c13922c66f011d384f290317dae480a17fc","tid":1497261,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"現今人手一支智慧型手機，它不僅可以幫我們解決生活中的大小事，現在甚至連男友的行蹤都可以追蹤的一清二楚！近日有日本節目介紹智慧型手機鮮少有人知道的功能，能有效查出另一半是否「出軌」，一瞬間就能查出對方曾經去過的50個地點，節目一播出後，立刻掀起討論話題。<br />\n <br />\n日本富士電視台節目《レディース有吉》近日介紹一個iPhone的隱藏版功能，不用安裝任何其他的app，只需4個步驟就可得知伴侶近幾個月的所有行蹤。節目以「如何知道男朋友最近到底去了哪裡？」為題，針對使用iPhone的用戶做出教學。首先打開「設定」找到「隱私權」選項，接著再打開「定位服務」，並找到「系統服務」，點進去後會看到「重要位置」，驗證成功後就完成了。<br />\n <br />\n其實「重要位置」也就是代表頻繁前往的地點，用戶只需要經過臉部或指紋辨識，就可以馬上看到過去50天去過的所有地點，更驚人的是，不管是詳細的地址還是時間，甚至就連造訪次數都看的一清二楚，儼然成為追蹤伴侶行蹤的神功能。節目還特別找來幾對夫婦進行測驗，發現他們均有疑似出軌或去過色情場所的紀錄，還讓其中一對夫婦的妻子崩潰痛哭，丈夫見狀也只好趕緊跪地求饒。<br />\n <br />\n節目一播出後，不少網友都表示超震驚，因為他們怎麼樣都沒想到iPhone居然還有這樣恐怖的功能，因此許多網友也紛紛表示「這就是我為什麼不買iPhone的原因」、「幸好我不是用iPhone」、「好可怕，女生都要變成名偵探柯南了」、「完全無所遁形呢」、「下次不敢再去聲色場所了」。"},{"pid":"a12f2eaffc6c1d0e001f5f856c808e7593cf795b","tid":1497261,"uid":131696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7676eed2d77fc73385d962cd012f9c01166fc7bb","tid":1497261,"uid":46014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"應該整文宣呼籲狗乸check狗手機<br />\n以我所知好多狗都有叫雞/有sp"},{"pid":"cb04382d8c27fda7b31a2bc0a58430b746432094","tid":1497261,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7676eed2d77fc73385d962cd012f9c01166fc7bb","tid":1497261,"uid":46014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"應該整文宣呼籲狗乸check狗手機<br />\n以我所知好多狗都有叫雞/有sp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"勞煩文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b11de08a37369813b53c1daca638e7150967469","tid":1497261,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:45:42.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁，咁顛<br />\n即off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d68f3573b15e68330fb72d32965971bd478a52","tid":1497261,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f441db20aac26ea7d59e696058cc435188c58d","tid":1497261,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:51:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeNRktU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeNRktU</a>"},{"pid":"51c5476d46b9f2829fdc5eb4924c10cab339d709","tid":1497261,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"已關閉功能 thx"},{"pid":"3c16ef7f9af06abe60437499b35b59523b356b3d","tid":1497261,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:55:01.000Z","msg":"睇左，但其實唔準，好多只係附近地方，係咪GPS問題？"},{"pid":"ccdfc40210cde006e1549f735c05a4ccc7e85807","tid":1497261,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"Google map 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42af441d7fba65b7076a76778b355cf36e2d4f33","tid":1497261,"uid":133525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦，反正都冇女check 你手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s